* Launch docker container -             #docker run -dit --name webos -p 80:80 centos:7
* Go inside the container -             #docker attach webos
* Install httpd inside the container -  #yum install httpd -y
* Create the webpages -                 #vi /var/www/html/index.html -> "this is my website hosted on container"
* Start the webserver -                 #/usr/sbin/httpd - Start the server
